{"metadata":{"externalID":"c:@F@samSelectDetailRegion","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"samSelectDetailRegion","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"samSelectDetailRegion"}],"symbolKind":"func","roleHeading":"Function","modules":[{"name":"DotDocument"}],"title":"samSelectDetailRegion","role":"symbol"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/DotDocument\/documentation\/DotDocument"]]},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"int","preciseIdentifier":"c:I"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"samSelectDetailRegion"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"const"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"SamColorImage","identifier":"doc:\/\/DotDocument\/documentation\/DotDocument\/sam_color_image","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@sam_color_image"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"image"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"const"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"int","preciseIdentifier":"c:I"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"detectedObjectBoundingBox"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"int","preciseIdentifier":"c:I"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"selectedBoundingBox"},{"kind":"text","text":");"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"return-value","text":"Return Value","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"0 on success, or a non-zero error code on failure.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Analyzes the input image and identifies the most suitable 200x200 pixel","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"region (bounding box) with high level of details that intersects a given bounding box.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"code":"detectedObjectBoundingBox","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is empty (width or height is 0), any region can be selected. Otherwise,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the selected region should have non-empty intersection with this bounding box. The selected region","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"should lie fully inside the input image.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If there is no region satisfying these conditions - if image width or height is smaller than 200","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"or ","type":"text"},{"code":"detectedObjectBoundingBox","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" lies outside the image, the selected bounding box will be (0, 0, 200, 200).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":null,"code":["                                  a bounding box in the format (x, y, width, height)."],"type":"codeListing"},{"syntax":null,"code":["                                  return, contains the bounding box in the format (x, y, width, height),","                                  where width and height are always set to 200."],"type":"codeListing"}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/dotdocument\/samselectdetailregion"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/DotDocument\/documentation\/DotDocument\/samSelectDetailRegion"},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://DotDocument/documentation/DotDocument/sam_color_image":{"role":"symbol","title":"sam_color_image","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"sam_color_image"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/DotDocument\/documentation\/DotDocument\/sam_color_image","kind":"symbol","abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/dotdocument\/sam_color_image","type":"topic"},"doc://DotDocument/documentation/DotDocument/samSelectDetailRegion":{"url":